WEBVTT

00:00:06.208 --> 00:00:09.760
♪Holding hands silently
as flowers fall and winds rise♪

00:00:10.432 --> 00:00:13.536
♪Dark tresses cascade like mountains.
Dreams intertwine♪

00:00:13.536 --> 00:00:17.856
♪Painting realms, clouds in palm,
my brushwork for you♪

00:00:18.048 --> 00:00:22.112
♪Light and shadow overlap
my name across time and space♪

00:00:22.272 --> 00:00:25.960
♪Across starry rivers,
I chase dreams afar♪

00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:30.624
♪Arms spread wide,
falling through heaven and earth♪

00:00:30.760 --> 00:00:33.280
♪The rhythm of breath and heartbeat♪

00:00:33.440 --> 00:00:38.464
♪A meeting of the souls♪

00:00:39.168 --> 00:00:43.424
♪Through shifting seas and lands,
I'd know you still♪

00:00:43.840 --> 00:00:47.800
♪Eyes bright as moonlit skies,
untouched by worldly dust♪

00:00:48.032 --> 00:00:51.680
♪Smiling gazes write eternity♪

00:00:51.680 --> 00:00:56.768
=The Crush=

00:00:57.235 --> 00:00:59.721
=Episode 10=
(Resurrection and Undying Devotion)

00:01:10.520 --> 00:01:11.880
My lady, you're finally awake.

00:01:11.880 --> 00:01:12.880
Thankfully, you're okay.

00:01:12.880 --> 00:01:14.280
If something had happened to you,

00:01:14.280 --> 00:01:16.000
I wouldn't have known what to do.

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:19.120
How did I get back here?

00:01:19.600 --> 00:01:21.720
The yamen officers brought you back.

00:01:21.960 --> 00:01:23.120
Where is Zixuan?

00:01:24.200 --> 00:01:25.040
He...

00:01:26.720 --> 00:01:27.320
He's...

00:01:27.400 --> 00:01:28.120
What's wrong?

00:01:28.120 --> 00:01:29.080
In the courtyard.

00:01:37.240 --> 00:01:37.880
Madam.

00:01:39.960 --> 00:01:41.600
Foam in his nose and mouth.

00:01:42.640 --> 00:01:44.760
A blood clot on the neck.

00:01:46.360 --> 00:01:47.280
He died from drowning.

00:01:49.280 --> 00:01:50.080
Drowning?

00:01:50.880 --> 00:01:51.440
Drowning?

00:01:52.680 --> 00:01:53.400
He's drowned?

00:01:53.760 --> 00:01:54.160
Yes.

00:01:54.520 --> 00:01:55.320
Madam.

00:01:56.160 --> 00:01:57.000
He looked for you

00:01:57.000 --> 00:01:57.800
with worry.

00:01:58.240 --> 00:01:59.520
When he reached the riverbank,

00:01:59.520 --> 00:02:00.600
he jumped into the river.

00:02:00.800 --> 00:02:02.120
He pulled you out of it,

00:02:02.680 --> 00:02:04.960
but he sank down.

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:06.440
Madam.

00:02:07.160 --> 00:02:08.360
This matter remains unclear.

00:02:09.160 --> 00:02:10.480
Considering it's kidnapping,

00:02:10.960 --> 00:02:12.720
I'll treat it as a homicide case.

00:02:13.200 --> 00:02:13.720
The body

00:02:14.200 --> 00:02:15.400
will be taken to the morgue.

00:02:16.440 --> 00:02:17.040
Take it away.

00:02:23.480 --> 00:02:24.000
Young Master!

00:02:25.920 --> 00:02:26.600
Young Master!

00:02:29.920 --> 00:02:30.760
He's gone.

00:02:30.760 --> 00:02:31.560
Young Master.

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:35.600
Who will make the Top Tea with me?

00:02:39.320 --> 00:02:39.760
Madam.

00:02:40.840 --> 00:02:41.920
In my opinion,

00:02:43.520 --> 00:02:46.240
Zixuan's death might actually

00:02:46.560 --> 00:02:48.320
be advantageous for you.

00:02:51.960 --> 00:02:52.920
What are you implying?

00:02:55.320 --> 00:02:56.160
With Zixuan drowned,

00:02:56.640 --> 00:02:58.080
Wei Xiaotang simply needs to remarry

00:02:59.360 --> 00:03:01.160
to be as effective as

00:03:01.160 --> 00:03:02.320
making the Top Tea.

00:03:04.760 --> 00:03:06.280
- Young Master.
- You're an NPC?

00:03:07.760 --> 00:03:08.560
Madam.

00:03:09.200 --> 00:03:11.720
Your mission has become much simpler.

00:03:14.280 --> 00:03:15.160
Young Master.

00:03:24.440 --> 00:03:25.520
All I need is to remarry,

00:03:28.480 --> 00:03:30.040
and I can complete the mission?

00:03:32.840 --> 00:03:34.080
Just remarry.

00:03:35.720 --> 00:03:37.480
- Young Master.
- Just remarry.

00:03:37.920 --> 00:03:39.760
Young Master.

00:03:41.640 --> 00:03:42.000
My lady.

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:43.240
Just remarry.

00:03:45.680 --> 00:03:46.200
Young Master.

00:04:05.240 --> 00:04:06.640
(Spare me your righteous)

00:04:06.640 --> 00:04:08.160
(posturing.)

00:04:08.520 --> 00:04:09.520
(In this world,)

00:04:10.040 --> 00:04:11.560
(everything can be traded)

00:04:11.560 --> 00:04:12.880
(to get what we want.)

00:04:15.240 --> 00:04:18.520
(Are we truly allies?)

00:04:20.120 --> 00:04:23.240
(I help you secure the position
as head of the Li family,)

00:04:23.800 --> 00:04:27.040
(and you help me win the Top Tea title.)

00:04:29.080 --> 00:04:30.160
(So, our relationship)

00:04:30.720 --> 00:04:32.160
(is all about a deal?)

00:04:34.600 --> 00:04:35.680
(Li Zixuan.)

00:04:36.280 --> 00:04:37.920
(Why are you being so stubborn?)

00:04:38.120 --> 00:04:40.080
(Don't fixate on trifles.)

00:04:41.240 --> 00:04:42.840
(This is not a trifle.)

00:04:43.320 --> 00:04:44.880
(It's a dirty trick.)

00:04:48.480 --> 00:04:49.480
(Anyway,)

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:53.200
(we are connected by contract marriage.)

00:04:53.720 --> 00:04:55.680
(Don't pretend we're in love.)

00:04:58.920 --> 00:05:01.080
(My goal is to win the Top Tea title.)

00:05:01.120 --> 00:05:02.880
(If I fail, I can't return home.)

00:05:03.640 --> 00:05:04.880
(Then stay with me)

00:05:05.280 --> 00:05:07.280
(until we win the Top Tea title.)

00:05:10.040 --> 00:05:11.680
(Making the Top Tea with you)

00:05:12.120 --> 00:05:13.400
(still holds promise.)

00:05:15.040 --> 00:05:16.320
(Xiaotang is my wife.)

00:05:17.000 --> 00:05:19.040
(From now on, anyone in the household)

00:05:19.760 --> 00:05:21.040
(must respect Xiaotang.)

00:05:21.920 --> 00:05:22.720
(You hear me?)

00:05:36.560 --> 00:05:38.040
Li Zixuan is dead.

00:05:42.240 --> 00:05:44.360
Li Zixuan is dead.

00:05:45.760 --> 00:05:49.040
Wei Xiaotang just needs to remarry

00:05:50.920 --> 00:05:52.280
to complete the mission.

00:05:55.680 --> 00:05:56.800
In that case,

00:05:58.000 --> 00:05:59.720
my mission has actually become simpler.

00:06:06.640 --> 00:06:07.440
Good.

00:06:09.800 --> 00:06:10.680
This way,

00:06:12.480 --> 00:06:14.320
I can return home

00:06:16.560 --> 00:06:18.040
and leave this place earlier.

00:06:28.864 --> 00:06:31.320
(Li's Tea Estate)

00:06:31.320 --> 00:06:33.160
Tang, you've suffered so much.

00:06:33.520 --> 00:06:35.000
I'll take you home right now.

00:06:35.760 --> 00:06:36.880
Don't worry.

00:06:37.200 --> 00:06:37.840
I will

00:06:38.200 --> 00:06:40.120
find you a better husband.

00:06:40.640 --> 00:06:41.960
If you don't wish to remarry,

00:06:42.120 --> 00:06:43.480
you can stay at home.

00:06:44.040 --> 00:06:45.200
I'll support you.

00:06:45.560 --> 00:06:46.360
Madam.

00:06:48.000 --> 00:06:48.800
Ning An.

00:06:49.560 --> 00:06:50.400
I came

00:06:50.560 --> 00:06:51.360
to bid you farewell.

00:06:51.360 --> 00:06:51.880
Ning An,

00:06:51.960 --> 00:06:53.280
stand up and talk.

00:06:53.680 --> 00:06:54.480
Madam.

00:06:55.520 --> 00:06:56.400
Since I was a child,

00:06:56.400 --> 00:06:57.840
I've served Young Master.

00:06:58.800 --> 00:07:00.360
Now that he's gone,

00:07:00.920 --> 00:07:02.640
I must leave too.

00:07:03.960 --> 00:07:04.960
I came

00:07:05.720 --> 00:07:06.960
to bid you farewell.

00:07:07.800 --> 00:07:08.440
Enough.

00:07:08.440 --> 00:07:08.880
Ning An,

00:07:09.040 --> 00:07:11.560
stop kneeling and get up now.

00:07:13.120 --> 00:07:14.680
Stand up and talk.

00:07:17.760 --> 00:07:19.000
After we leave,

00:07:20.480 --> 00:07:21.720
take good care of yourself.

00:07:25.560 --> 00:07:26.360
We're leaving.

00:07:27.360 --> 00:07:28.760
Madam, there's one thing.

00:07:31.440 --> 00:07:33.600
This is what Young Master gave to me

00:07:34.280 --> 00:07:35.400
before saving you.

00:07:36.240 --> 00:07:37.800
He ordered me to give it to you

00:07:38.480 --> 00:07:39.880
no matter what happened.

00:07:48.512 --> 00:07:50.016
(Contract)

00:08:02.600 --> 00:08:03.560
Get in the carriage.

00:08:16.040 --> 00:08:16.640
I have to go.

00:08:22.200 --> 00:08:22.760
Madam.

00:08:23.320 --> 00:08:24.520
Take care, Madam.

00:08:27.920 --> 00:08:28.400
My lady.

00:08:54.464 --> 00:08:58.048
(Li's Tea Estate)

00:09:07.480 --> 00:09:08.280
Wait!

00:09:09.760 --> 00:09:10.640
Get in!

00:09:22.960 --> 00:09:23.480
Tang.

00:09:30.080 --> 00:09:33.840
(Today, Li Zixuan and Wei Xiaotang
made a contract.)

00:09:34.560 --> 00:09:35.720
(The terms are as follows:)

00:09:37.440 --> 00:09:39.920
(Wei Xiaotang shall help Li Zixuan
secure the family business.)

00:09:40.800 --> 00:09:42.800
(In return, Li Zixuan shall)

00:09:43.280 --> 00:09:44.400
(entrust Wei Xiaotang)

00:09:44.600 --> 00:09:46.360
(with the management of the tea estate.)

00:09:47.200 --> 00:09:49.800
(Wei Xiaotang's authority shall
be absolute in all matters.)

00:09:50.280 --> 00:09:51.280
(No objections allowed.)

00:09:53.000 --> 00:09:54.920
(Upon claiming the title of Top Tea,)

00:09:55.720 --> 00:09:58.840
(Li Zixuan shall get closer
with Wei Xiaotang.)

00:10:25.888 --> 00:10:31.424
(Morgue)

00:10:41.240 --> 00:10:42.120
Xiaotang,

00:10:42.600 --> 00:10:43.520
what brings you here?

00:10:46.840 --> 00:10:48.360
I need you to revive Li Zixuan.

00:10:50.960 --> 00:10:51.800
Xiaotang,

00:10:52.160 --> 00:10:53.240
if I may be blunt,

00:10:53.560 --> 00:10:55.640
remarrying would be an easier path.

00:10:55.880 --> 00:10:57.480
Save your concern for me.

00:10:57.480 --> 00:10:59.160
I need you to revive Li Zixuan.

00:11:01.280 --> 00:11:03.800
Alright. Don't regret this choice.

00:11:04.600 --> 00:11:05.480
Just for the record,

00:11:06.080 --> 00:11:08.200
my method works only once.

00:11:08.400 --> 00:11:09.480
Are you certain about it?

00:11:15.680 --> 00:11:16.480
Yes.

00:11:29.600 --> 00:11:32.200
The buds down the hill soak
in the shallow stream.

00:11:32.200 --> 00:11:34.560
The sandy path
under the shade of the trees is clean.

00:11:34.920 --> 00:11:36.920
Evening rains patter as cuckoos sing.

00:11:37.280 --> 00:11:39.560
Who claims youth cannot be reclaimed?

00:11:39.840 --> 00:11:41.760
See the stream before my door
flow westward!

00:11:42.280 --> 00:11:44.760
Don't lament the swift passage of time
in your old age.

00:12:27.840 --> 00:12:29.400
My lady, you're finally awake.

00:12:30.600 --> 00:12:31.280
My lady.

00:12:31.280 --> 00:12:32.080
Li Zixuan!

00:12:33.040 --> 00:12:34.600
Foam in his nose and mouth.

00:12:35.240 --> 00:12:38.160
A blood clot on the neck.
He died from drowning.

00:12:38.240 --> 00:12:39.040
Drowning?

00:12:39.240 --> 00:12:40.280
He's not dead yet!

00:12:51.200 --> 00:12:51.880
Well...

00:12:51.880 --> 00:12:52.720
Young Master...

00:13:09.560 --> 00:13:10.720
Li Zixuan!

00:13:11.800 --> 00:13:13.080
You can't die!

00:13:15.040 --> 00:13:15.840
Li Zixuan!

00:13:16.960 --> 00:13:17.760
Li Zixuan!

00:13:17.960 --> 00:13:18.760
Wake up!

00:13:20.280 --> 00:13:22.560
Our contract remains unfulfilled!

00:13:23.400 --> 00:13:24.800
You are not allowed to die!

00:13:29.040 --> 00:13:30.200
You are not allowed to die!

00:13:30.720 --> 00:13:31.720
You mustn't die!

00:13:32.280 --> 00:13:33.760
My mission isn't done yet!

00:13:34.000 --> 00:13:35.120
Do you hear me?

00:13:35.520 --> 00:13:36.560
Li Zixuan!

00:13:44.000 --> 00:13:44.880
He is awake!

00:13:44.920 --> 00:13:45.440
Li Zixuan.

00:13:46.840 --> 00:13:47.640
You're awake.

00:13:48.680 --> 00:13:49.560
Thank heavens.

00:13:49.720 --> 00:13:51.560
They say
that when husband and wife are united,

00:13:51.560 --> 00:13:52.480
anything can be done.

00:13:52.480 --> 00:13:53.600
It must be my lady's love

00:13:53.600 --> 00:13:55.040
for Mr. Li that worked miracles.

00:13:55.240 --> 00:13:56.800
That's why Mr. Li came back to life.

00:13:56.960 --> 00:13:58.240
This is simply miraculous!

00:13:58.760 --> 00:13:59.920
Yes.

00:14:05.840 --> 00:14:07.640
Young Master.

00:14:10.920 --> 00:14:11.720
Thank you.

00:14:13.320 --> 00:14:13.880
My pleasure.

00:14:13.960 --> 00:14:14.960
You scared us.

00:14:14.960 --> 00:14:16.360
I didn't expect your rescue method

00:14:16.960 --> 00:14:18.760
to be straight out of a romantic drama.

00:14:20.200 --> 00:14:22.120
Young Master, how are you feeling now?

00:14:24.880 --> 00:14:26.120
I'm fine.